    "html": "<!-- Template HTML do Arrendamento -->\n<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 800px; margin: auto;\">\n  <h1 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">CONTRATO DE ARRENDAMENTO</h1>\n  \n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">1. Partes</h2>\n    <h3>Primeiro Outorgante - Senhorio:</h3>\n    <div class=\"party-info\">\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Nome:</strong> <span id=\"landlordName\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{landlord.name}}</span></span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>NIF:</strong> <span id=\"landlordVat\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{landlord.vat}}</span></span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Estado Civil:</strong> <span id=\"landlordMaritalStatus\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{landlord.maritalStatus}}</span></span></p>\n      <p><strong>Residência:</strong> <span id=\"landlordAddress\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{landlord.address}}</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <h3>Segundo Outorgante - Arrendatário:</h3>\n    <div class=\"party-info\">\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Nome:</strong> <span id=\"tenantName\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{tenant.name}}</span></span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>NIF:</strong> <span id=\"tenantVat\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{tenant.vat}}</span></span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Estado Civil:</strong> <span id=\"tenantMaritalStatus\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{tenant.maritalStatus}}</span></span></p>\n      <p><strong>Residência:</strong> <span id=\"tenantAddress\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{tenant.address}}</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">2. Objeto do Contrato</h2>\n    <p>O Senhorio dá de arrendamento ao Arrendatário, que aceita, o seguinte imóvel:</p>\n    <div class=\"property-info\">\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Fração:</strong> <span id=\"propertyFraction\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{property.fraction}}</span></span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Andar:</strong> <span id=\"propertyFloor\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{property.floor}}</span></span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Destino:</strong> <span id=\"propertyDestination\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{property.destination}}</span></span></p>\n      <p><strong>Endereço:</strong> <span id=\"propertyAddress\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\"><span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{property.address}}</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"page-break\"></div>\n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">3. Prazo e Renda</h2>\n    <div class=\"payment-info\">\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Prazo do Contrato (meses):</strong> <span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{contract.duration}}</span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Valor da Renda Mensal (€):</strong> <span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{contract.monthlyRent}}</span></p>\n      <p class=\"inline\"><strong>Caução (€):</strong> <span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{contract.deposit}}</span></p>\n      <p><strong>Forma de Pagamento:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{contract.paymentMethod}}</span></p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">4. Início do Contrato</h2>\n    <p>O presente contrato tem início em <span id=\"contractStartDate\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\">[Data de Início]</span>.</p>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">5. Obrigações do Arrendatário</h2>\n    <p>O Arrendatário obriga-se a:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Pagar a renda até o dia <span style=\"background-color: orange; color: #fff; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px;\">{{rentDueDay}}</span> de cada mês</li>\n      <li>Conservar o imóvel em bom estado</li>\n      <li>Não fazer obras sem autorização do Senhorio</li>\n      <li>Não dar ao local outro fim que não o estabelecido</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">6. Encargos e Despesas</h2>\n    <p>São da responsabilidade do Arrendatário:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Consumos de água, luz, gás e outras utilidades</li>\n      <li>Despesas de condomínio</li>\n      <li>Pequenas reparações de conservação</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">7. Lei Aplicável e Foro</h2>\n    <p>O presente contrato rege-se pelas leis portuguesas e, em caso de litígio, as partes elegem o foro do local do imóvel.</p>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h2 class=\"clause\">Local e Data</h2>\n    <p><span id=\"contractDate\" contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"editable\">[Data]</span></p>\n    \n    <h2 class=\"clause\">Assinaturas</h2>\n    <div class=\"signatures\">\n      <div class=\"signature-block\">\n        <p><strong>Senhorio:</strong></p>\n        <span id=\"landlordSignature\">__________________________</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"signature-block\">\n        <p><strong>Arrendatário:</strong></p>\n        <span id=\"tenantSignature\">__________________________</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <style>\n    .section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }\n    .clause { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem; color: #1a1a1a; }\n    .inline { display: inline-block; margin-right: 1rem; }\n    .editable { border: 1px dashed #999; border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 6px; min-width: 50px; display: inline-block; }\n    .input-field { border: 1px solid #999; border-radius: 4px; padding: 4px 8px; width: 120px; margin: 0 4px; }\n    .input-field-large { border: 1px solid #999; border-radius: 4px; padding: 4px 8px; width: 300px; margin: 0 4px; }\n    .signatures { margin-top: 3rem; }\n    .signature-block { margin-bottom: 4rem; }\n  </style>\n</div>",
    "price": 15,
    "downloadPrice": 2.5,
    "icon": "fa-file-contract"
  }
